{"id":3343,"date":"2025-01-28T12:04:35","date_gmt":"2025-01-28T12:04:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/?p=3343"},"modified":"2025-01-28T12:08:05","modified_gmt":"2025-01-28T12:08:05","slug":"nhs-tayside-charitable-foundation-supports-kanzen-for-life-with-25000-funding-boost","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/2025\/01\/28\/nhs-tayside-charitable-foundation-supports-kanzen-for-life-with-25000-funding-boost\/","title":{"rendered":"NHS Tayside Charitable Foundation Supports Kanzen for Life with \u00a325,000 Funding Boost"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"3343\" class=\"elementor elementor-3343\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f09f71f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"f09f71f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8571225 elementor-hidden-desktop dce_masking-none elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8571225\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/473442965_598574136129193_8133110173207279981_n-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3344\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/473442965_598574136129193_8133110173207279981_n-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/473442965_598574136129193_8133110173207279981_n-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/473442965_598574136129193_8133110173207279981_n-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/473442965_598574136129193_8133110173207279981_n-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/473442965_598574136129193_8133110173207279981_n.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db04d90 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"db04d90\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-ogsc=\"rgb(0, 36, 81)\">\n<p>Kanzen for Life, a leading Dundee-based charity dedicated to empowering communities through physical activity, wellbeing, education and social connection, is pleased to announce a new partnership with the NHS Tayside Charitable Foundation. The foundation has generously awarded \u00a325,000 in funding to support Kanzen for Life\u2019s purpose of creating healthier and more connected communities.<\/p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:387\">Kanzen for Life focuses on addressing some of the most deep-rooted issues in society, emphasizing preventative work and early intervention to reduce future health and social care costs. With thousands of children, adults and families participating in weekly activities, the charity&#8217;s work directly aligns with NHS Tayside&#8217;s vision of tackling health inequalities and promoting wellbeing.<\/p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"9:1-9:63\"><strong>Roy O\u2019Kane, Charity Chief Officer of Kanzen for Life, said:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:469\">\u201cThis partnership with the NHS Tayside Charitable Foundation highlights the importance of preventative investment in community health. By addressing challenges such as inactivity, isolation, and poor mental health at their root, we can deliver change that benefits individuals and the wider community. This funding will enable us to expand our reach and impact at a time when it is needed most. We are very grateful to the foundation for their support and partnership.\u201d<\/p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:87\"><strong>Shelley McCarthy, Charity Chief Officer of NHS Tayside Charitable Foundation, said:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"15:1-15:271\">&#8220;We are proud to announce the \u00a325,000 contribution to Kanzen for Life, a testament to our commitment to supporting innovative solutions that enhance lives and promote well-being. Together, we are paving the way for a brighter, healthier future for the people of Tayside.&#8221;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<div data-ogsc=\"rgb(0, 36, 81)\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The foundation has awarded \u00a325,000 in funding to support Kanzen for Life\u2019s purpose of creating healthier and more connected communities.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":3344,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[12,6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3343","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-case-study","category-projects"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3343","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3343"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3343\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3348,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3343\/revisions\/3348"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3344"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3343"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3343"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3343"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}